            <tr>
                <td height="20"></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td style="padding: 0 40px;font-size: 17px;line-height: 25px; "><b>Hi! <%= company_name %>
                    </b>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td height="20"></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td style="padding: 0 40px;font-size: 17px;line-height: 25px; ">I hope this message finds you well. As
